WEBVTT

00:00:00.645 --> 00:00:02.015
Dakle, na fakultetu,

00:00:03.349 --> 00:00:04.913
studirao sam političke nauke,

00:00:04.937 --> 00:00:07.399
što znači da sam morao da napišem
mnogo seminarskih.

00:00:07.423 --> 00:00:09.471
Sad, kad normalan student piše seminarski,

00:00:09.495 --> 00:00:11.868
mogao bi da započne s radom
malčice nalik ovome.

00:00:11.892 --> 00:00:13.043
Znate -

00:00:13.067 --> 00:00:14.724
(Smeh)

00:00:14.748 --> 00:00:16.575
započinjete možda nešto sporije,

00:00:16.599 --> 00:00:18.567
no završite dovoljno posla
u prvoj nedelji

00:00:18.591 --> 00:00:20.422
pa, kad krenu teži dani kasnije,

00:00:20.446 --> 00:00:22.603
sve se završi, sve ostaje uljudno.

00:00:22.627 --> 00:00:23.829
(Smeh)

00:00:23.853 --> 00:00:26.124
I ja bih želeo tako da radim.

00:00:26.148 --> 00:00:27.342
To bi bio plan.

00:00:27.366 --> 00:00:29.856
Sve bih pripremio,

00:00:29.880 --> 00:00:32.374
ali onda, zapravo,
došao bi red na seminarski